## Common Commands (Troubleshooting)
run this on browser 



### Activate Virtual Environment (Windows)

```powershell
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

### Install Required Packages

```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn pydantic tldextract numpy pandas scikit-learn xgboost joblib python-multipart
```

---

### Install from requirements.txt

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

### Update pip

```bash
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
```

---

### Run the FastAPI Backend

```bash
uvicorn dashboard_url:app --reload
```

---

### If Uvicorn is Not Installed

```bash
pip install uvicorn
```

or

```bash
python -m uvicorn dashboard_url:app --reload
```

---

### If FastAPI is Missing

```bash
pip install fastapi
```

---

### If tldextract is Missing

```bash
pip install tldextract
```

---

### Check Installed Packages

```bash
pip list
```

---

### Check Python Version

```bash
python --version
```

---

### Generate requirements.txt

```bash
pip freeze > requirements.txt
```

---

### Backend API Documentation

Open in your browser:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

---

### If the Backend Shows "Connection Refused"

1. Activate the virtual environment:

```powershell
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

2. Start the server:

```bash
uvicorn dashboard_url:app --reload
```

3. Verify the server is running by visiting:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```